name: Dogewhale
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
Dogewhale is a protocol with a deflationary token backed by multi-doge reserves. It contributes to various philanthropy causes and as a member of the Doge Alliance, it integrates gamified quests with the purpose of building up DeFi across crypto.

The multi-doge reserve allows token holders to claim 10% of its value at pre-established checkpoints. Checkpoint 1 starts at $12500. In the last checkpoint, 100% of the value can be redeemed by holders.
